654
00:33:33,880 --> 00:33:35,679
- Bueno, él es Brad.
- Hola.

655
00:33:36,714 --> 00:33:37,781
Hola.

656
00:33:37,782 --> 00:33:39,443
Soy Courtney.

657
00:33:39,751 --> 00:33:42,481
- Brad. Feliz Navidad.
- Feliz Navidad.

658
00:33:43,554 --> 00:33:44,578
